Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:30.72,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}オレンジ映したプリズム
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:30.72,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}照耀出橘色的光暈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:38.83,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}自分のすべてを許せるくらいに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:38.83,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}能夠原諒自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:47.14,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}優しくなりたい 君のために
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:47.14,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了你 我想變得如此溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:55.25,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この世界にあふれる光だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:55.25,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}將洋溢於這世界的所有光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.35,0:01:00.66,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}両手のなか集めて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.35,0:01:00.66,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}聚集在雙手中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:06.05,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}暗闇さえも 照らし出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:06.05,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即便是黑暗處 也能給予光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:09.25,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}長く続く道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:09.25,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在漫長持續的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:12.29,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}迷わないように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:12.29,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}能夠不迷失方向

Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:23.76,ED_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悲しいときほど笑う私を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:23.76,ED_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}越是悲傷越是展露笑容的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:35.44,ED_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何も言わないで抱いてくれたね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:35.44,ED_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你不發一語的抱住了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:42.24,ED_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}凍りついたドアがそっと開くような
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:42.24,ED_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彷彿像是冰凍的門扉漸漸溶開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:48.98,ED_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そんな気がしたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:48.98,ED_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}給了我這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:55.38,ED_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君に逢えてうれしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:55.38,ED_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}能與你相遇 真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:22:01.98,ED_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}孤独さえも分かち合えた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:22:01.98,ED_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使是孤獨 也一同分享
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.06,0:22:08.90,ED_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今もこの空の下つながっていると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.06,0:22:08.90,ED_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在仍在這片天空下緊緊相連著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:17.67,ED_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そう思える 離れても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:17.67,ED_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我仍這麼的想 即使分隔兩地

Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要取消？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在阿尔富汗的失态\N我们也有听闻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想说我把事情搞砸了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种会把\N重要商品丢下逃走的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法信任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信任是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，多亏那小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我连打工都打不成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也该回归本业了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#18 深海派对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.89,0:02:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是文化祭的入口门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说去年的主题是“和平”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，今年的主题是“保安”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这道门可兼为维护治安的\N观测与防卫据点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算全副武装的恐怖份子\N前来袭击文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这道门的设计\N能撑住相当长的一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次出差回来以后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的战争痴呆\N是不是越来越严重了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你们也都不觉得奇怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是赞同相良所说的\N“让来参加文化祭的人能感到安心”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:03:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到这种东西会感到安心的\N只有宗介好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，也许我们是有点和平痴呆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个\N“入场欢迎门制作费147万1000元”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未免也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔，你发现这部分了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该可以用超低价买到\N以色列制的复合装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常至少也要花500万…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛突然打我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭全部的预算是150万耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果照你所说的去做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校什么活动都办不成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一能看到的就是\N耸立在正门的这个阴森森的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之，我是不会同意这东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是现在不立刻撤走的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,标识装置被误触启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个颜料对人体无害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在说这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在感到悲哀啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再有第二次的宝贵青春岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然得跟这种完全不体贴的\N战争痴呆男吵吵闹闹的渡过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高二的夏天\N对女孩子来说可是特别的季节耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在开学前的这一个礼拜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在家里\N安安静静地混吃等死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说你这礼拜很闲是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要跟我一起去南方岛屿？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们两人去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是认真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就想邀你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来慰劳你们啰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在气氛正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会做奇怪的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会做奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不危险吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你这么坚持的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我陪你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟，你还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？不要紧，不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然夏天还是适合蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像太大胆了点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带这件去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你大概也只有\N学校泳装之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件也带去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单独两人去会不会不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，反正对方是宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做错事都不太可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(把夏天的回忆保存起来喔 BY恭子)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到相良会这么大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当作是夏末的一次小小冒险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,识别不明舰，持续保持冲撞路线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜…潜航后依然持续接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，为什么不躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方应该也发现了才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离100
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离50
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离30
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员随便找个东西抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失得无影无踪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查BQQ-5，快去\N说不定这就是传闻中的“TOY BOX”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于幽灵潜水艇的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体积非常的大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不声不响的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不声不响的消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且速度快得惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果刚才遇到的是\N那艘“TOY BOX”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船的舰长\N一定是个性格扭曲的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下三烂的疯狂家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份大礼我一定会还你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎么了？舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了有点对不起“巴萨狄那”的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他不要太沮丧才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的话\N自尊心一定会大大受创吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没有演习的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有成果了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将一般前进时的静音性\N再往下方修正一点或许比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，我们回基地去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然会赶不上生日宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，明天岛上有客人要来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要坐这个去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了你而准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，我真的对你刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你准备得这么周到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，我们要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去Mithril西太平洋部队基地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰丝塔罗莎上校想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线路E2传来任务讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收讯完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马德加斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回基地要暂缓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宴会也要中止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样往南方前进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地的海域是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昂柳群岛是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟化学武器有关
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状况是储藏设施\N被某武装集团袭击占领
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人感到可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那座化学武器储藏库\N遭到爆破的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么事情就会很严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小国可能会遭到毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美军应该会派\N装备AS的特殊部队过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样能解决就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良宗介士官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么不满的话\N希望你能说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽可能的加以改善
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔，如果是这件事的话\N反正你是不可能解决得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良士官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽达岛传来通讯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:09:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B待机？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说要你尽快赶来\N航行中的De Danaan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要也要一起过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟也？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是平民耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是泰莎的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换个方向想想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,De Danaan可说是\N世上最安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就带她一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有带泳装吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上是有带啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它换上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以去客舱的后方换
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换完后\N把手提行李放进这个袋子里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点，没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那身打扮…该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我帮你穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么啦\N士官，还有一分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:10:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:11:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了，无法重来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，到底要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后会有期？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会想从这里跳下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚蓝的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚蓝的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单独两人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认着水了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着水后的人在水面胡乱挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到激烈的打水声与尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把声音传到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手，千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰唆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:12:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有丝毫考虑到我的心情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉下去吧，你这个呆头鹅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临Tuatha De Danaan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从飞机上被推下来，被丢到海里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再咕噜咕噜的潜到水里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了某个士官大人之外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人都会累的，真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想请你到美丽达岛基地的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为状况有点改变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也想见泰莎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你也有很多事想谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，那也是原因之一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良士官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，上校大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你去主机库一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管跟谁都好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我跟他说一声\N“我等一下就过去”好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能请你先换回便服？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在带你去参观舰内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很窄对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在潜舰中\N这样算是很宽的通路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也考虑到紧急时\N必须奔跑的乘员安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏这种设计
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这里少了很多\N因为撞到东西而跌倒的蠢蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点小事不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫人看得冒冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是舰长吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你这么说，我实在有点羞愧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我家一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有我不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不包括乘员的隐私
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，请往这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然小要你可能\N不太喜欢这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立正
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向当泰丝塔罗莎上校与部队\N濒临种种危机时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现其勇气、行动力\N以及深厚人情的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟要小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致上最高的谢意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道小要你要来以后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家说无论如何都想表示敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到很光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我没有做那么伟大的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:14:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是独当一面的士兵\N都无法轻易做到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你感到自傲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马德加斯中校说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么欢迎仪式就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来会在这里\N举办一场小型派对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请小要也要一起参加喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派对？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是这孩子的一岁生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来喔，来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了舰内宾果大会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣耀的头奖开奖时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个很棒的奖品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话，我很想要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个奖品就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰丝塔罗莎舰长的热吻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威巴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没听说有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“有什么我能帮忙的请尽管说喔”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明这么说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实是有说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换成提供\N“爱用内衣”之类的也可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我更不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就热吻啰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长也说OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O的65
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是第五次了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有听牌的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸…幸福的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，重新振作精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续下一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…竟然要接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:16:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N的42
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边也听牌了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,场面越来越热闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利的女神究竟会对谁微笑呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马卡兰吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦或是梁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B的13
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了，各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宾果啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头奖得主竟然是马卡兰上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长，热情一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，跟我热吻不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:17:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然，舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深感光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是我这辈子\N最棒的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真走运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是ECHO-84，被击中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求救！求救！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚被击中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来支援一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，那个红色的家伙\N竟然把波布给…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来救救我，救…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会有这种蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没子弹了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景气真差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便告诉你，你是最后一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才虽然也有个\N哭着求饶的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦了，阿兵哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来示范给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然真的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身材又好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,品味也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她身边的男人\N当然不会放过她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样，那你为什么要叹气？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是担心他们闹得太凶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘潜舰可是在执行作战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还演奏音乐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么脱节的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是泰莎说可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为小兵的你没资格\N说什么有的没的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管经历过多少次的战役
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，星条旗永远飘扬是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群家伙似乎到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.74,0:20:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有情报传来\N他们在海上与突袭部队会合了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群有礼貌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧的咬住我们的鱼饵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有之前的那两人\N可能也一起坐上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔，那对情侣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不错，太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们跟Mithril的家伙们\N一起死掉的话不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让那女的死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外事故总是会发生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舰内的浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全裸的毛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对全裸的小要与泰莎所吐露出的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤裸裸的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.86,0:22:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火热热的全裸肌肤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把本大爷的活跃紧紧的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回 FULL METAL PANIC\N「ENGAGE SIX SEVEN」


